<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Service Agreement - <%= agreementNumber %></title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
      .container {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      header img {
        max-width: 150px;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
      }
      h1,
      h2 {
        color: #000000;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }
      .details,
      .terms,
      .signature {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 2px solid black;
        border-radius: 30px;
        background-color: #fbce44;
      }
      .details p,
      .terms p,
      .signature p {
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      .service {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #999;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header class="header-container">
        <img src="logo.png" alt="Company Logo" />
        <h1>Service Agreement #<%= agreementNumber %></h1>
      </header>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <section class="details">
            <h2>Provider Details</h2>
            <p><strong>Provider Name:</strong> <%= provider.providerName %></p>
            <p><strong>ABN:</strong> <%= provider.abn %></p>
            <p>
              <strong>Address:</strong> <%= provider.address.street %>, <%=
              provider.address.city %>, <%= provider.address.state %> <%=
              provider.address.postalCode %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= provider.phone %></p>
          </section>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <section class="details">
            <h2>Customer Details</h2>
            <p>
              <strong>Name:</strong> <%= customer.user.first %> <%=
              customer.user.last %>
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong><%= customer.referenceName %></strong> <%=
              customer.referenceNumber %>
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Address:</strong> <%= customer.address.street %>, <%=
              customer.address.city %>, <%= customer.address.state %> <%=
              customer.address.postalCode %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <%= customer.mobile %></p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="details service">
        <h2>Service Details</h2>
        <p><strong>Product:</strong> <%= product.name %></p>
        <p><strong>Total Units:</strong> <%= product.quantity %></p>
        <p><strong>Cost:</strong> <%= totalPrice %></p>
        <p><strong>Agreement Beginning:</strong> <%= startDate %></p>
        <p><strong>Agreement Ending:</strong> <%= endDate %></p>
      </section>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <section class="signature">
            <h2>Customer Signature</h2>
            <div>
              <img
                width="50%"
                src="<%= customerSignature %>"
                alt="Customer Signature"
              />
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <section class="signature">
            <h2>Provider Signature</h2>
            <div>
              <img
                width="50%"
                src="<%= providerSignature %>"
                alt="Provider Signature"
              />
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="terms">
        <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>

        <ul class="timeline">
          <% for (var i = 0; i < provider.termsAndConditions.length; i++) { %>
          <li class="timeline-yellow">
            <div class="timeline-time">
              <h3><%= provider.termsAndConditions[i].heading %></h3>
              <p><%= provider.termsAndConditions[i].paragragh %></p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <% } %>
        </ul>

        <p>
          <strong>Service Provision:</strong> We're excited to provide you with
          the service described in this agreement at a time that works for both
          of us. Just remember, if you need to cancel an appointment, please
          give us at least 7 days' notice to avoid charges to your NDIS plan.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Confidentiality:</strong> Your privacy matters to us! We
          promise not to share your personal information with others without
          your consent. However, there might be rare situations where the law
          requires us to disclose information to ensure someone's safety, even
          without your permission.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Courtesy and Respect:</strong> We believe in treating each
          other with courtesy and respect, and we kindly ask you to do the same.
          We understand that everyone has tough days, but please remember that
          abusive language or threats are not acceptable and may lead to service
          termination or even police involvement.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Cancellation or Suspension of Service:</strong> Feel free to
          cancel or suspend this service agreement at any time by sending us a
          written notice. If you just need a break, suspending the agreement
          lets you take some time off without fully canceling the service.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Feedback:</strong> We'd love to hear your thoughts about our
          service! Whether it's a compliment or a complaint, your feedback helps
          us improve. Please don't hesitate to let us know, contact us after an
          appointment, or visit circlesupports.com to submit your feedback for
          review and follow-up.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Travel:</strong> We charge travel time up to 1 hour to and
          from an appointment and the home base of a worker. Where workers see
          multiple customers in the same region, we aim to fairly apportion this
          cost. We charge the NDIS rate for Kilometers travelled which is
          updated in line with the NDIS price guide.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Invoicing:</strong> After delivering services, we'll send an
          invoice to your plan manager. If you'd like a copy for yourself, just
          let us know, and we'll happily provide one.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="footer">
        <img width="5%" src="../../client/public/logo.png" />
        &copy; 2024 Circle Independent. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
